google_endpoints_service.description: Creates and rolls out a Google Endpoints service.

service_name.description: The name of the service.  Usually of the form `$apiname.endpoints.$projectid.cloud.goog`.

openapi_config.description: The full text of the OpenAPI YAML configuration as described [here](https://github.com/OAI/OpenAPI-Specification/blob/master/versions/2.0.md).

grpc_config.description: The full text of the Service Config YAML file (Example located [here](https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/python-docs-samples/blob/master/endpoints/bookstore-grpc/api_config.yaml)).

protoc_output_base64.description: The full contents of the Service Descriptor File generated by protoc.  This should be a compiled .pb file, base64-encoded.

project.description: The project ID that the service belongs to.  If not provided, provider project is used.
